Pre-Game Insights: The Stake Stars and Summits Trophy is planned to begin on October 17, 2024, with three T20Is between Team USA and Team Nepal at the Grand Prairie Cricket Stadium in Grand Prairie, Texas.
Miscellaneous Highlights: This collaboration represents yet another key milestone in the development and marketing of cricket in the United States.
Others: Stake will also serve as the title sponsor for the upcoming USA vs Nepal cricket series, the Stake Stars and Summits Trophy.
